The fork dates from 2026-05-19. Significant additions in Patron:
  - Polish locale and SYSTEM_PROMPT for Polish legal practice
  - Zero-cloud self-host (Supabase + MinIO, no Cloudflare R2)
  - 6 Polish and EU legal MCP connectors (mcp-saos, mcp-nsa, mcp-isap,
    mcp-krs, mcp-eu-sparql, mcp-eu-compliance - all MIT-licensed,
    separate repositories)
  - Hash-chain audit trail (AI Act art. 12 compliant)
  - Constitution AI v1.0.0 and Implementation Playbook (governance/)
  - Modular chat layer (lib/chat/* - 12 modules from monolithic chatTools.ts)
  - Vitest test suite (69 tests in 6 files)
  - Docker compose deployment + multi-stage Dockerfiles
  - LibreOffice in-container support for .docx → .pdf

